How to run the game ðŸŽ®

1. Clone repository : https://github.com/Jonesey86/Whac-a-Mole

2. Open Open the solution file (`Whack-a-Mole.sln`) in Visual Studio Code.

3. Rebuild solution.

4. Run the game.

ðŸŽ® How to play Whack A Mole video game ðŸŽ®

1. Start the Game

- Click Start button.

  2.How to play the game
  Every 2 seconds a Mole and a Piranha plant will appear on screen, Player has to hit the Mole as many times as possible and avoid Piranha plant .

3. Win or Reset
   The game detects wins or loss and displays the result.

_Click Reset to restart the game_.

